-08T15:55:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">讀vtc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  恥笑開始</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 讀得掂VTC嘅AE先講嘢啦 乜撚都笑<br />\n望下前面速大等緊你喇HKCC英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf901d44514d789b2cecad37fc60c12499521f0e","tid":110180,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:57:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">讀vtc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  恥笑開始</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 讀得掂VTC嘅AE先講嘢啦 乜撚都笑<br />\n望下前面速大等緊你喇HKCC英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔撚駛問我讀乜 我要入就隨時入到HKCC嘅<br />\n想笑鳩HKCC就隨撚便<br />\nIVE AE有巴打隨時靠Intern入機電署咁好景唔通又同你講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n發你嘅大達啦去 不過睇死你現實一定係一個無乜存在感嘅HKCC死毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}